  Word(id: '6-1079', korean: '디자인', english: 'design', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '좋은 디자인은 기능과 미학의 조화입니다.', exampleTranslation: 'Good design is a harmony of function and aesthetics.', pronunciation: 'dijain', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
  Word(id: '6-1080', korean: '색채', english: 'color; coloring', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '색채의 조합이 작품의 분위기를 결정합니다.', exampleTranslation: 'The combination of colors determines the mood of the work.', pronunciation: 'saekchae', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
  Word(id: '6-1081', korean: '구도', english: 'composition (art)', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '안정적인 구도가 시각적 균형을 만듭니다.', exampleTranslation: 'A stable composition creates visual balance.', pronunciation: 'gudo', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
