  Word(id: '6-1083', korean: '명암', english: 'light and shadow; chiaroscuro', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '명암 대비가 극적인 효과를 만들어냅니다.', exampleTranslation: 'Light and shadow contrast creates dramatic effects.', pronunciation: 'myeongam', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
  Word(id: '6-1084', korean: '원근법', english: 'perspective (art)', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '르네상스 시대에 원근법이 발전했습니다.', exampleTranslation: 'Perspective developed during the Renaissance era.', pronunciation: 'wongeunbeop', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
  Word(id: '6-1085', korean: '비엔날레', english: 'biennale', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '베니스 비엔날레는 세계적인 미술 행사입니다.', exampleTranslation: 'The Venice Biennale is a world-renowned art event.', pronunciation: 'biennalle', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
  Word(id: '6-1086', korean: '아방가르드', english: 'avant-garde', level: 6, partOfSpeech: 'noun', example: '아방가르드 예술은 기존 관습에 도전합니다.', exampleTranslation: 'Avant-garde art challenges existing conventions.', pronunciation: 'abanggareudeu', category: 'Art & Aesthetics'),
